  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\nIf a lot of items should be shown with markdown, it applies only for some of them in the start and in the end of the message.\nREproducible with Android only(tried with Android 8 and Android 9)\n\n#### Expected behavior\nMarkdown is applied to all items\n\n#### Actual behavior\n![no_markdown](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/69146479-3eb8df80-0ad0-11ea-874b-acb89c8ce1ff.gif)\n\n[Payload](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1xWtryiYHfifCuJF5MtIxC7WXCxp9_pkXOkVpCH1Ju3k/edit?usp=drivesdk)\n\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\n###Steps to reproduce\n- Open Status\n- Join public chat\n- Send message with several items with markdown (i.e. with 100 `__bold__`)\n\n### Additional Information\n\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\n- Status version: nightly 18/11/2019\n- Operating System: Android",
